products.title: Bakeware Set
products.body_html: Make healthier baking a piece of cake with our ceramic-coated bakeware. The Complete Bakeware Set includes 11 pieces, all free of toxic chemicals, so you can get to baking goods without any of the bads. Sets include storage organizers to keep your kitchen tidy.

products.title: Utensil Set
products.body_html: Stir in only the good stuff. Our Wooden Spoon, Server, Scraper, Spatula, and Tongs are crafted from responsibly grown birch wood free of toxic materials. Condense your drawer with these versatile essentials, designed to maximize the life of ceramic-coated pans. Plus, their sleek silhouettes perfectly complement Caraway Cookware, enhancing both function and style in your kitchen. That's the recipe for success.

products.title: Stock Pot
products.body_html: A lightweight workhorse. Made with our signature non-stick and non-toxic ceramic coating, our 12 qt Stock Pot adds significant capacity for bigger batches. It’s the first non-stick Stock Pot of its kind with a ceramic-coated interior, meaning you won’t have food simmering in forever chemicals for hours. Lid included.

products.title: Rondeau
products.body_html: Our Rondeau is the MVP of one-pan meals, made with our signature non-stick, non-toxic ceramic coating. Thanks to the high, straight walls, you can simmer, braise, or fry without a mess. And the large surface area is perfect for browning before finishing in the oven. With two stainless steel handles, easily move your dish from the stove, to the oven or the table. Lid included.

products.title: Petite Cooker
products.body_html: Simplify sides with Caraway's Petite Cooker — its two-quart capacity is ideal for steaming rice, cooking grains, or preparing sauces. Shop it here.

products.title: Medium Cutting Board
products.body_html: Slice & dice without letting microplastics into your food. This medium-sized non-toxic Cutting Board is made with FSC-certified birch wood and finished with food-safe mineral oil & wax. And the best part? The board’s backside features recessed grooves around the entire perimeter that can catch excess liquid if cutting juicy food such as fruit or meats.

products.title: Large Cutting Board
products.body_html: Slice & dice without letting microplastics into your food. This large non-toxic Cutting Board is made with FSC-certified birch wood and finished with food-safe mineral oil & wax. Use it to carve a rotisserie chicken or cut up a watermelon. And the best part? The recessed handle grooves perfectly attach onto Food Storage containers, so you can easily transfer food.

products.title: Knife Set
products.body_html: Stay sharp in the kitchen. Our Chef's Knife, Prep Knife, Bread Knife, & Paring Knife are crafted with premium German Stainless Steel blades and have a professional-grade Rockwell Hardness score of 58+. The Kitchen Shears, which can detach for easier cleaning, add further versatility for quickly snipping herbs or slicing open your meal kit delivery box. With balanced weight and an ergonomic design, you’ll be able to easily chop anything on the menu.

products.title: Stir Fry Pan
products.body_html: Our take on a wok, the Stir Fry Pan is an all purpose pan that features our signature non-stick, non-toxic ceramic coating. The high sloped walls allow you to spread food and concentrate heat onto different ingredients, cooking vegetables, grains, and proteins all at once. It’s the perfect pan for cleaning out the fridge, so your favorite foods never go to waste. 12” Glass Lid sold separately.
